DEERE & COMPANY, Plaintiff-Appellant, v. KUBOTA CORPORATION and Kubota Tractor Corporation, Defendants-Cross Appellants. No. 02-1607, 02-1625. United States Court of Appeals, Federal Circuit. July 17, 2003.

Before NEWMAN, LOURIE, and SCHALL, Circuit Judges.

JUDGMENT

PER CURIAM.

This CAUSE having been heard and considered, it is ORDERED and ADJUDGED: AFFIRMED. See Fed. Cir. R. 36
